Package: liblpttrigger0
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Homepage: http://cnbisrv02.epfl.ch
Description: Library to provide an raw and easy access to parallel port
 This library provides a unified interface to set the pins of the parallel
 port. It implements an easy way to send triggers on the parallel port as well
 as a simple pulse width modulation generator.
 
Package: liblpttrigger0-dev
Provides: liblpttrigger-dev
Conflicts: liblpttrigger-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: liblpttrigger0 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Homepage: http://cnbisrv02.epfl.ch
Description: Library to provide an raw and easy access to parallel port
 This library provides a unified interface to set the pins of the parallel
 port. It implements an easy way to send triggers on the parallel port as well
 as a simple pulse width modulation generator.
 .
 This package contains the files needed to compile and link programs which
 use lpttrigger.
